1000004201460@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Let ⌊×p(y|x)×⌋ be the ⌊>conditional probability>⌋ distribution function of ⌊/Y/⌋ given ⌊/X/⌋.@@@@1@12@@oe@26-8-2013
1000004201470@unknown@formal@none@1@S@We will consider ⌊×p(y|x)×⌋ to be an inherent fixed property of our communications channel (representing the nature of the ⌊∗⌊>noise>⌋∗⌋ of our channel).@@@@1@23@@oe@26-8-2013
